{"tid":1761520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(Old news) 不滿聯合國逼退台灣 列根罵非洲國「猴子」","createTime":"2019-11-29T03:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T04:20:08.000Z","uid":40267,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"81f832c64b81cd2a2b24d3a9164defd0589229b5","tid":1761520,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:37:41.000Z","msg":"記者 彭惠筠 報導 2019/08/01 21:12<br />\n<a href=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/08/01/20190801174759-529da944.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F01%2F20190801174759-529da944.jpg&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=a6c4c85a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/08/01/20190801174759-529da944.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n圖／達志影像美聯社 美國總統川普，最近談到巴爾的摩，再引發種族歧視風波。而今天<br />\n有一個機密錄音檔曝光，當時擔任加州州長的美國前總統雷根，因為不滿台灣被逼退聯合<br />\n國，居然用「猴子」來形容當時轉支持中國的非洲國家代表。 川普槓上民主黨非裔大老<br />\n，口出種族歧視言論，但現在連已經過世的前總統雷根都被挖出，曾經私下大罵非洲國家<br />\n的人是「猴子」，電話錄音檔首度曝光。 前美國總統雷根vs.尼克森：「看到那群猴子，<br />\n來自那些非洲國家，可惡的他們，我看他們連穿鞋子都還很不自在吧，哈哈哈哈哈哈，然<br />\n後，還以為自己能主導大局，對吧，對，一切都反客為主了。」<br />\n<br />\n雷根說的就是在1971年聯合國大會上，許多非洲國家轉承認中國，導致台灣被迫退出，退<br />\n聯當時表決一通過後，非洲國家代表開心的手舞足蹈，當時立場挺台，還是加州州長的雷<br />\n根氣得打電話給尼克森大罵，說這一幕就像是猴子在跳舞，尼克森還大笑附和，而如今川<br />\n普為了選戰，也大打種族牌。   美國總統川普：「我是全世界最不種族歧視的人。」<br />\n川普，雷根同樣都是共和黨人，都打著要讓「美國再次偉大」的口號，踩上敏感的種族議<br />\n題紅線，川普的歧視風波，更成為民主黨人砲轟的箭靶。 民主黨黨內初選候選人卡斯楚<br />\n：「首先，川普總統是種族歧視者，這次又再度證明了這一點。」<br />\n<br />\n民主黨黨內第2波辯論，兩位候選人上台都大罵川普煽動歧視，分裂美國，這樣場面在<br />\n2020大選前恐怕會一再上演。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z7GLJsclRi8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz7GLJsclRi8&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=980ddd50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z7GLJsclRi8</a>"},{"pid":"9f1a098c66bb6d80ed879b31a1557ea015f2e752","tid":1761520,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b7e4285c3457b0d467892aac632b87728bfa1fc4","tid":1761520,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:41:23.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"cd5a836ff164fec5eb95db76f7ed35c52bbe15e9","tid":1761520,"uid":200280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"列根一早已經睇清楚非州係冇撚得救<br />\n希望Trump可以做埋列根未完成嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60c6527eb8f93e16a5314104dca25e658ae6291","tid":1761520,"uid":26332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"講得無錯，可惜現今左膠橫行，政治正確，自我審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cff456f7448ff9d778948a43f0cfebd61eb5e1","tid":1761520,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd5a836ff164fec5eb95db76f7ed35c52bbe15e9","tid":1761520,"uid":200280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"列根一早已經睇清楚非州係冇撚得救<br />\n希望Trump可以做埋列根未完成嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:46:59.000Z","msg":"小心三毛Cap你上reddit<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b384359458eba67ba3ad0e858b761326cdcaff8e","tid":1761520,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"關侵咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd054d298ddcd753fd937ce3b494e03683f2607","tid":1761520,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fAdRvno.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfAdRvno.png&h=519c1e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjeA7wk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjeA7wk.jpg&h=a5f5f4d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9776d60b2d9aec1a697ebb0d2a6dd6ab91b1f487","tid":1761520,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:52:49.000Z","msg":"唔好理美國內部問題，因為呢樣超出我地能力。我地要打人權民主中蟈威脅，爭取美國兩黨支持。"},{"pid":"ed506f42659656e426e39055019d1de0a96982c5","tid":1761520,"uid":265192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"客觀地講列根反共有功, <br />\n但種族歧視同政教合一有過<br />\n<br />\n香港人同中國人唔同既地方<br />\n就係香港作為文化同種族多元既國際城市<br />\n香港人理應有更進步既國際觀, 尊重唔同種族同文化"},{"pid":"253950a3e10186376a60a2927caa1baa6bc1d16f","tid":1761520,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"根本俾非洲國家主導聯合國係錯誤"},{"pid":"07e04197258f7643f46a01e5b31a611b63051ead","tid":1761520,"uid":274699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:54:26.000Z","msg":"當年會選列根既加州<br />\n<br />\n今日既加州<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7136c806b8f7da34647fb68f62a500596d29e5f","tid":1761520,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e04197258f7643f46a01e5b31a611b63051ead","tid":1761520,"uid":274699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:54:26.000Z","msg":"當年會選列根既加州<br />\n<br />\n今日既加州<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}